                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">Cute.  But somewhat unsportsmanlike.</div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Rating: </span>
                      <span>4</span>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Helpful: </span>
                      <span>2</span>
